stories.title: Not a complete washout
stories.subTitle: India v New Zealand, TVS Cup, Chennai
stories.summary: Only 26.5 overs of play was possible on a wet Chennai afternoon, but Tendulkar and Cairns ensured that at least a few hard-core fans went home with the hint of a smile on their faces

stories.title: Rain has the final word
stories.subTitle: India v New Zealand, TVS Cup, Chennai
stories.summary: Rain stopped play after 26.5 overs in the first match of the TVS Cup, giving India and New Zealand three points apiece from the abandoned game
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Samanth Subramanian
